# Local development environment for LoadLynx.
#
# Do not put Wi-Fi credentials in this file. Development firmware must receive
# Wi-Fi settings at runtime through USB/devd or Web Serial, then persist them in
# device EEPROM.
#
# Factory Wi-Fi builds are an explicit release/factory-only workflow. If that
# workflow is ever needed, provide LOADLYNX_FACTORY_WIFI_* through the build
# environment for that command only, not through repo-root .env.
